metadata.creator: Toby Fox
metadata.description:
Music from the RPG "Undertale", which was released on September 15, 2015. This rollicking rock tune plays during the boss fight with Sans, one of the game's three final bosses. Other versions of the song were previously featured in other works in which creator Toby Fox was involved.

(For those asking about how to download it, there's five download links over to the right. Just try using one of those.)
